0.8.dev
------------------------------

- introduce "--gendeploy" for generating a "etc" directory
  which contains supervisord configuration for running devpi-server
  and redis as two supervised processes, as well as an example
  nginx-devpi.conf for configuring an nginx site pointing to the service.

- fix issue4: keep the "changelog" thread active across
  network/reachability errors.  Thanks Laurent Brack.

- use argparse instead of optparse, simplify and group options

- fix python2.6 and simplify logging configuration

0.7
---

-  Initial release

